item.title: Item.cfg messed up my server
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

A good way to “debug” this would be to go into your ItemHandler and make it print out each line it is reading. When it errors, it would probably have either printed the line that errored or the one before it.

Your error itself is because one item has too many tabs and/or variables (for stats).
